Selenium Grid Commands:
Hub command : java -jar selenium-server-4.32.0.jar hub
Node command for standalone : java -jar selenium-server-4.32.0.jar node --detect-drivers true
Node command for another machine : java -jar selenium-server-4.32.0.jar node --detect-drivers true --publish-events tcp://192.168.0.103:4442 --subscribe-events cp://192.168.0.103:4443

Note: For Selenium grid if we want to add another machine as node to hub then both machines should be connected to same network then only it will connect

Link for native application gestures: https://github.com/appium/appium/blob/1.x/docs/en/writing-running-appium/android/android-mobile-gestures.md
Link : https://testsigma.com/docs/troubleshooting/mobile-apps/app-package-and-activity/